{"tid":541002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"$26雜嘜瓜　充北海道蜜瓜 正貨售$200　海關3店拘3人","createTime":"2018-01-26T04:12:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-26T05:52:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"fa3240c28b6d833a5bf557fcb2dfdfa3f44d5d27","tid":541002,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T04:12:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180126/20286212\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180126%2F20286212&d=6b8NNPeCEMRihft%2FqxBOAkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=72d66dd9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180126%2F20286212&h=ee0a68d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180126/20286212</a><br />\n<br />\n$26雜嘜瓜　充北海道蜜瓜<br />\n正貨售$200　海關3店拘3人<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】海關前日在旺角及深水埗3間水果零售商，撿獲68個疑假冒產地蜜瓜，估計市值約1,775元，拘捕2女1男店員（47至59歲）。該批附有「北海道」、「溫室」及日文標籤的蜜瓜，涉嫌聲稱產地與事實不符，每個平均售價約26元，與正貨約200元售價相差達7倍。<br />\n<br />\n記者：溫瑞麟<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n海關早前接獲舉報，指旺角及深水埗一帶有水果零售商出售假冒產地蜜瓜。海關前日派員放蛇試購，結果在3間水果零售商撿獲該批懷疑附有虛假產地標籤的蜜瓜，並拘捕3人。撿獲的蜜瓜附有「北海道」、「溫室」及日文標籤，與日本北海道一款蜜瓜的標籤幾乎一樣，不排除有不法商人偽造標籤，海關會追查該批蜜瓜來源及產地。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180126/large/26la6p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180126%2Flarge%2F26la6p1.jpg&h=52390272&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n假　海關撿獲的蜜瓜為黃色，外表較平滑。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180126/large/26la6p2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180126%2Flarge%2F26la6p2.jpg&h=dcb60591&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真　北海道蜜瓜外表有網狀紋。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180126/large/26la6p10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180126%2Flarge%2F26la6p10.jpg&h=08474ed6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n進濤菓欄負責人劉小姐<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n業界試食：味淡硬身少汁<br />\n<br />\n海關公佈撿獲假冒蜜瓜後，《蘋果》記者昨午到油麻地果欄了解，發現營業的20多檔中仍有一檔售賣疑似同款蜜瓜，但該店標示是「冰糖瓜」，該批冰糖瓜同樣附有「北海道」、「溫室」及日文標籤，放在店舖較高不顯眼位置，每個售25元，記者以顧客身份問及其出產地時，有職員透露是「日本品種大陸種植」，並強調是有客人訂貨訂多了才拿出來發售。<br />\n<br />\n記者買了一個冰糖瓜，拿給專賣日本水果的進濤菓欄負責人劉小姐試食，劉表示冰糖瓜味道較淡，少汁，口感較硬身，不是日本蜜瓜品種，「30蚊一個冇可能係日本蜜瓜」。<br />\n她指最近聽聞街巿有聲稱是「北海道溫室蜜瓜」出售，每個售價數十元，她指真正的北海道溫室蜜瓜當造時間是7月至11月，瓜身呈圓形，外表有網狀紋，非海關撿獲的橢圓形狀。<br />\n<br />\n她表示日本出產的蜜瓜味道偏甜，每個約200元。現時日本蜜瓜全部是「T字網紋」，主要來自熊本、靜岡、宮崎，瓜身有貼紙及編號，包裝盒外印有產品級次及產地等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n\t塔斯曼尼亞車厘子現假貨<br />\n港聞 4小時前"},{"pid":"4a5d35032efa798a89758c149a6a3a8245c1d621","tid":541002,"uid":139815,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T04:14:17.000Z","msg":"菓欄負責人劉小姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a86811d753dfa79b9814e4ff45ae75f32b2a5d8e","tid":541002,"uid":16250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T04:15:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6742dd1adbee4cde16b2adfe49eab3ff7b2009a9","tid":541002,"uid":45684,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T04:17:32.000Z","msg":"係咪Royal級"},{"pid":"ca15d6e6fc5327b2a7c1ee17a760a3c49bdd24d3","tid":541002,"uid":25514,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"6742dd1adbee4cde16b2adfe49eab3ff7b2009a9","tid":541002,"uid":45684,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T04:17:32.000Z","msg":"係咪Royal級"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T04:20:33.000Z","msg":"呢批都要識人先訂到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f006e2d9199c03af9fe43ed2988a674648fc306","tid":541002,"uid":51717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T04:21:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 噚晚就係經過深水埗見到，$25蚊一個冰糖瓜，諗住買完嘢返轉頭買個試試，但買完嘢唔記得咗件事。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n懷疑就係嗰檔俾人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"144a3bc3c64ce74d0b2e9f6642986583ddc4ced1","tid":541002,"uid":60977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T04:23:10.000Z","msg":"又係進濤"},{"pid":"4feebbf8a175f1a13145ace92707ffa904d62bc9","tid":541002,"uid":73454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T04:40:20.000Z","msg":"個樣同日本瓜差咁遠都呃到人😂"},{"pid":"b0f5fcfd19099fc1145451afc6f8d4c823a1beef","tid":541002,"uid":129235,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4feebbf8a175f1a13145ace92707ffa904d62bc9","tid":541002,"uid":73454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T04:40:20.000Z","msg":"個樣同日本瓜差咁遠都呃到人😂"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T04:52:05.000Z","msg":"因為大把無知婦孺唔知正版係乜野樣<br />\n我老母都係街邊生果檔買過好多次所謂日本蘋果<br />\n一望個樣未食已經知係大陸野但佢依然係被人呃完再呃"},{"pid":"6db17f9076ed5552c1edd91d8be08634d9446cd8","tid":541002,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0f5fcfd19099fc1145451afc6f8d4c823a1beef","tid":541002,"uid":129235,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4feebbf8a175f1a13145ace92707ffa904d62bc9","tid":541002,"uid":73454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T04:40:20.000Z","msg":"個樣同日本瓜差咁遠都呃到人😂"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T04:52:05.000Z","msg":"因為大把無知婦孺唔知正版係乜野樣<br />\n我老母都係街邊生果檔買過好多次所謂日本蘋果<br />\n一望個樣未食已經知係大陸野但佢依然係被人呃完再呃"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T05:16:14.000Z","msg":"最近見到百佳電視廣告賣<br />\n中國山東富士蘋果 $xx 平均2.45/個<br />\n<br />\n究竟係中國定係富士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af080555b68b01fd01a53e4bfb18d4f38618dd1e","tid":541